OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEx-Post Office boss regrets
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'subbies with their hand in
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fthe till' email            
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Former Post Office managing director   
OL,6, Alan Cook has said he will "regret for 
OL,7, the rest of my life" an email in which 
OL,8, he wrote that subpostmasters had their 
OL,9, "hands in the till".                   
OL,11,F"What I wrote in that email was        
OL,12,Funacceptable", Mr Cook told an inquiry 
OL,13,Finto the Horizon IT scandal.           
OL,15,FThe email, sent in 2009 to the Royal   
OL,16,FMail Group's press officer, said the IT
OL,17,Fwas "stable and reliable".             
OL,19,FMore than 900 sub-postmasters were     
OL,20,Fwrongly prosecuted due to the software.
